ygData.subject: Re: CAMPING
ygData.msgSnippet: Hey mike, I really have to agree with you here, places that were formerly void of players...and i mean like 1-5 other players in the zone are now abundant with
ygData.messageBody:
Hey mike,

I really have to agree with you here, places that were formerly void of
players...and i mean like 1-5 other players in the zone are now abundant
with would be campers. Lets look at lake rather, with lothaniel i could go
there with a group and be the ONLY plyers in that zone, it was great, now
when i go there with my cleric, there are at least 15 people in the zone. Ok
15 people isnt that much but they are usually cmping out where all the good
stuff is. I suppose thise thing is bound to happen, i mean everyone is
gaining levels and there are only so many areas to hunt in right? Well im
fine with that not much can be done, ill just go to solusek where its barren
and test my luck out there. Heck id rather have a little more people in the
dungeon to help me if i needed it ! hehe.
John Zwanenburg
